ave you ever felt like making content for the game? Well we feature a Content Creator system that if joined, grants you a unique badge to show of to fellow Monkes. If this game seems like something you wanna play, go ahead and download on the Meta Applab Store!", "short_description": "Welcome to Monke Tag, a Gorilla Tag fan game with Tag! There are 3 Game modes, Infection, Tag, and Casual. There are many maps to play in and explore. This game uses the Gorilla Locomotion System."}]}, "developer_name": "Monke Laboratory Studios", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://monkeylabstudios.wixsite.com/studio", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Monke Laboratory Studios", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://monkeylabstudios.wixsite.com/studio", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1573854509480616"}, {"id": "411892083130028"}, {"id": "394813081514456"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "25850274364586808"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035344_1956832518100406_1382433572107163388_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=100&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=xmy89XA2YDAQ7kNvgFxXoHI&_nc_ht=scontent.oculuscdn.com&_nc_gid=Abw9H3VIbluvdJaNcNQoOTv&oh=00_AYDIKwg15ObF6PCYhG_f7dPAEaei6iVCnB7RHV-2_YD5yA&oe=66CF22FD"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Monke Tag", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF",